title: Deafheaven's George Clarke On The Darkness At Heart Of 'New Bermuda'
text: Deafheaven's George Clarke On The Darkness At Heart Of 'New Bermuda' Tuesday, 20 October 2015 (7 minutes ago) The band's singer and lyricist explains how moving to Los Angeles led to the depression and frustration that fuel Deafheaven's ferocious new album.
